Photo shared by MINDSET THERAPY™ on July 29, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee have 3 hours of 1. Deep Work UNDISTRACTED work every day. No social media, no email, no phone. Staying focused and removing distractions iS key if you want to accomplish more.'.

Photo shared by MINDSET THERAPY™ on July 29, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 2. Wake Wake up and go to bed at the same time every day It increases your energy levels and builds discipline. I've woken up at 5 AM and slept at9 at PM 6 days out of the week tor for the past 5-6 years.'.

Photo shared by MINDSET THERAPY™ on July 29, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 3. Delayed gratification too much partying, TV shows, video games, unhealthy food, etc will ruin your motivation. Work hard now and make short term sacrifices for your long term goal and the future life you want.'.

Photo shared by MINDSET THERAPY™ on July 29, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 4. Work out MINIMUM 3 times a week to train your body, but more importantly, train your mind. Exercising regularly builds discipline, resilience and increases your energy. The key is to be consistent with it.'.

Photo shared by MINDSET THERAPY™ on July 29, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be an image of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 5. How you do one thing is how you do everything. If you don't give 100% to your workouts, you're not going to give 100% to your business. Treat everything with excellence and see how your life changes.'.

Photo shared by MINDSET THERAPY™ on July 29, 2021 tagging @richardyuzee. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Richard Yu @richardyuzee 6. Practice gratitude. Take time to give thanks every day.l pray to God and thank him daily for the life and opportunity He's given me.'.
